description: Try our easy to follow Chicken Tikka Sticks & Fennel Raita recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Chicken Tikka Sticks & Fennel Raita Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Thread the chicken on to 12 bamboo skewers that have been soaked in water for at least 20 minutes and place them on a foil-lined grill rack. Cook under a preheated grill for 8-10 minutes, turning once, until browned and the chicken is cooked through. Serve 2 skewers per person with the raita.
